data.value:
* All books were numbered one by one according to the subfields suitable for their content and placed in the relevant bookshelves. An example library layout is shown on the side. The number ranges written next to the library floors are representative, please get the "library, floor and number" information according to the search results you have made in the programme. To give an example: when the result that a book's number you are looking for is 60 on the 2rd floor of the clinical psychology bookshelf, you can find this book labeled "K - 60" on the second floor of the clinical psychology bookshelf.
* Subfield abbreviations were generally tried to be given with first letter, but since there were the same first letter some abbreviations with the first two letters or different types were reproduced (based on Turkish).
Sosyal(S) - Sözlük(Sö); Öğrenme - Ö; Öteki Alt Alanlar (Öt); Klinik (K) - Karışık(-);
